            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿الٓمٓ﴾: سَبَقَ الكلامُ على الحُرُوفِ المُقَطَّعةِ في أوَّلِ سُورَةِ البَقَرةِ.</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "32:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَا رَيۡبَ فِيهِ﴾: لاشَكَّ فِيه.</h2>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "32:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَمۡ يَقُولُونَ﴾: بل أيقُولُ المشرِكُونَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿ٱفۡتَرَىٰهُ﴾: اختَلَقَ محمدٌ ﷺ القرآنَ مِن تِلْقاءِ نَفْسِهِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿نَذِيرٖ﴾: أي: رَسُولٍ مُنْذِرٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "32:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱسۡتَوَىٰ عَلَى ٱلۡعَرۡشِ﴾: عَلَا وارْتَفَعَ سُبْحَانَه وَتَعَالَى عَلَى عَرْشِهِ كَما يَليقُ بِجَلَالِهِ.</p>\n<p>﴿ٱلۡعَرۡشِ﴾: هُوَ سَريرُ المُلْكِ الَّذي اسْتَوى عَلَيهِ الرَّحْمَنُ، وَتَحْمِلُهُ الملائِكَةُ، وَهْوَ أَعْظَمُ المْخلُوقاتِ، وهو سَقْفُ الجنَّةِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَلِيّٖ﴾: ناصِرٍ يَنْصُرُكُم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿تَتَذَكَّرُونَ﴾: تَتَّعِظُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "32:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يُدَبِّرُ ٱلۡأَمۡرَ﴾: يَقْضِي القَضَاءَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿يَعۡرُجُ﴾: يَصْعَدُ.</h2>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "32:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "32:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَحۡسَنَ كُلَّ شَيۡءٍ﴾: أَحْكَمَهُ وأَتْقَنَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿طِينٖ﴾: تُرَابٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "32:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿نَسۡلَهُۥ﴾: ذُرِّيَّتَه.</h2>\n<h2>﴿سُلَٰلَةٖ﴾: نُطْفَةٍ مَسْلُولَةٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَهِينٖ﴾: ذَلِيلٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "32:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿سَوَّىٰهُ﴾: أتمَّ خَلْقَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةَ﴾: القُلُوبَ.</h2>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "32:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ضَلَلۡنَا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ﴾: هَلَكَتْ أجْسَادُنا وتَفَرَّقَت وصِرْنا تُرَاباً.</p>\n<h2>﴿كَٰفِرُونَ﴾: مُنْكِرُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "32:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَتَوَفَّىٰكُم﴾: يَقبِضُ أَرْوَاحَكُم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وُكِّلَ بِكُمۡ﴾: وُكِّلَ بِقَبْضِ أرْوَاحِكُم.</h2>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "32:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿نَاكِسُواْ رُءُوسِهِمۡ﴾: أي: مُطْرِقُوها خِزْياً وَنَدَامَةً.</p>\n<h2>﴿مُوقِنُونَ﴾: مُصَدِّقُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "32:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿هُدَىٰهَا﴾: رُشْدَها، وَتَوفِيقَها لِلْإِيمانِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿حَقَّ﴾: وَجَبَ وثَبَتَ.</h2>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "32:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡخُلۡدِ﴾: الدَّائِمِ.</h2>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "32:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يُؤۡمِنُ﴾: يُصَدِّقُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ذُكِّرُواْ بِهَا﴾: وُعِظُوا بِها.</h2>\n<h2>﴿خَرُّواْ﴾: سَقَطُوا.</h2>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "32:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَتَجَافَىٰ﴾: تَرْتَفِعُ وتَتَنَحَّى.</h2>\n<p>﴿عَنِ ٱلۡمَضَاجِعِ﴾: عَنِ الفُرُشِ الَّتِي يُضْطَجَعُ عَلَيها.</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "32:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مِن قُرَّةِ أَعۡيُنٖ﴾: مِن موجِباتِ المسَرَّةِ والفَرَحِ.</h2>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "32:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
